    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels brand new? You\u2019ve got to check this one out! It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it\u2019s like it just rolled off the showroom floor. The interior is spotless, the paint is gleaming, and it runs like a total dream. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I know you\u2019re going to love it the second you see it. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by for a test drive!",
      "price": 44500.0,
