    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered icon, presenting in showroom condition with a documented service history that prioritizes mechanical longevity. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six remains a masterpiece of atmospheric induction, featuring precision-tuned individual throttle bodies and a fully overhauled double-VANOS system. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Crucially, the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearings have been addressed\u2014eliminating the primary failure points of this chassis. The suspension remains taut, preserving the original kinematics and communicative steering rack feel. This is a turn-key collector-grade vehicle for the discerning driver who demands peak longitudinal and lateral performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
