    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car is in showroom condition, featuring a flawless exterior with a deep, lustrous paint finish that has been ceramic coated and kept strictly in a climate-controlled garage. There are absolutely no rock chips, door dings, or curb rash on the pristine alloy wheels. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather remains supple with no bolstering wear, and the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty liners since day one. Every electronic feature and driver-assist system functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives like it just left the dealership floor. Complete with all original keys, manuals, and a clean title in hand.",
      "price": 48500.0,
