      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this car\u2014it is an absolute gem! Honestly, it\u2019s in such flawless condition that it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this ride since day one, and it drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically perfect and ready for a new home, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look or have any questions at all!",
