    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This collector-grade AP2 S2000 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. Under the hood, the F22C1 inline-four remains factory-spec, delivering linear power delivery with an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain features a precise six-speed close-ratio manual transmission paired with a Torsen limited-slip differential for optimal torque biasing. The chassis is impeccably preserved, retaining its original double-wishbone suspension geometry and rigid X-bone frame integrity. Every factory VIN tag is present on the original body panels, and the finish is free of imperfections. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key example for the purist who demands surgical handling and high-revving engagement.",
